{"tid":97312,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有無人好憎拜年 我年年逗得三百蚊","createTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-27T17:26:32.000Z","uid":30594,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"bbdae89f4bb2516d1bc4248838255c0c826778f1","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:33:13.000Z","msg":"老豆年年都屌鳩我唔撚去拜年 話無禮貌 <br />\n屌你咩 年年去睇人面色 ,唔撚同人地講野班親戚又話我啞 新年流流講啲好野得唔得？<br />\n最撚火滾就係上人啲富豪屋企，你老母 坐係到睇住你地班撚樣係到撚狗，撚雀 撚完先去食， 我坐係到都唔知做乜鳩。<br />\n最慘就係 等咁撚多粒鐘 先得300蚊人工 我留係屋企打飛機唔好？乞兒啊？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2ddab702e479fa0678fc5468e006bb004a84e8a7","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:34:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6e5f75cba85c78cf59cf24722f2a62bdc7169920","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:35:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"bae4c9c41ea66a55e4403314e09aa1fc85522709","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:36:37.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0b8bae331d1d657c2d390608416e4488336d22c1","tid":97312,"uid":35324,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:37:07.000Z","msg":"我呢啲毒撚好憎新年！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班親戚都唔熟，年齡接近嗰堆得我一個係圈子外面，佢地會一齊出街玩同成日傾計，但我永遠唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新年又要格硬坐埋一齊，毒坐成兩個幾鐘食餐飯，食完又要聽佢地傾計<br />\n傾傾下可能又問我啲野，我邊及得上你地啲叻仔叻女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌新年呀！！！！！"},{"pid":"6ecd233726435550c75ce760d138922d5173b179","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:39:51.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>我呢啲毒撚好憎新年！！！<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n成班親戚都唔熟，年齡接近嗰堆得我一個係圈子外面，佢地會一齊出街玩同成日傾計，但我永遠唔會<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n新年又要格硬坐埋一齊，毒坐成兩個幾鐘食餐飯，食完又要聽佢地傾計<br />\n傾傾下可能又問我啲野，我邊及得上你地啲叻仔叻女呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我屌新年呀！！！！！</blockquote><br />\n屌 同你一鳩樣  我都唔撚同啲親戚熟 就連叫佢地做乜我都唔撚知  成日都問埋啲on9問題 知佢地叻知佢地有錢 問佢老母啊"},{"pid":"c6ba5190e6826ecb3bbf4479e55ba9cbeac96619","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:43:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cf897cc5a4d7e2990de2c1dbaf7fd2553b2f0e38","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:45:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"63944501e41c92e353f00c130b465e5128690f0f","tid":97312,"uid":5908,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:46:46.000Z","msg":"同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾面屋企人坐一個鐘走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8b017e96dc6ac1576feaad3aabfe06d4dcc1af3e","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:49:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾面屋企人坐一個鐘走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 坐成大半日啊我 搭車出去又個幾兩個鐘 睇佢地撚雀又幾個鐘 等野食 等佢地傾計又幾粒鐘 媽啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"609a57b67c4afbcc42902703d410f4ba21870849","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T14:49:40.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>同感<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n俾面屋企人坐一個鐘走人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\nBtw 就算比人屌 我都唔撚會去"},{"pid":"e4b7e83f82749c458acea96546d7f669e2647b8b","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:26:47.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c684f7b0197a13c8b97faba4b15218630b4e9f59","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T15:56:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"855bb53af6c03ffba24b49a79176678a3858cae3","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:26:22.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b271a8ce3c7279d92adf62b27ee96be8e28beae4","tid":97312,"uid":30594,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-27T17:26:32.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/a